{"tid":1537070,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該大家咪撚再睇金水","createTime":"2019-09-03T19:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T20:46:06.000Z","uid":169396,"like":93,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6042a4ea440a259efda895808617c1abc26a71ed","tid":1537070,"uid":169396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:56:40.000Z","msg":"條撚樣大事大非喺到fake news ，一段字一張whatsapp圖就當係FC左。<br />\n<br />\n勝在自己個page多人like就日日假消息，佢啲料全部都係抄呢到抄嗰到，全部網民爆料黎。利申已經唔係第一次俾佢呃鳩左<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/yhmetblogspot/posts/2559306244119498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fyhmetblogspot%2Fposts%2F2559306244119498&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3GVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=8f93e687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/yhmetblogspot/posts/2559306244119498</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">之前已經俾人捉過幾次Fake News</span><br />\n<br />\n今日太子手足佢又係一句傷者情況暫時ok就完post 見俾人屌冇FC就po左張whatsapp對話圖上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/edW7Ayd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FedW7Ayd.png&h=de7cb707&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁其他人當然係繼續屌一張圖就FC到啊？咁我都有屌左幾句咁啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qfRCXM7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqfRCXM7.png&h=64a92883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後我就俾佢del晒留言，仲block左唔俾我留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">拒絕流料 請大家唔好再睇金水</span></span>"},{"pid":"bb2b17201f73a478d73b6f4af3a24167c220510b","tid":1537070,"uid":169396,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:59:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我知你冇義務去做呢啲，但你個page咁多人like可唔可以FC左先唔好呃啲真係緊張手足狀況嘅人</span></span>"},{"pid":"12555d97c651e5a878480d342d8b9701f0798aad","tid":1537070,"uid":169396,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:00:54.000Z","msg":"金水你del人cm又block質疑你真假嘅手足 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你同中共咩分別啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"d91d6efcdbf1ba49ed9eaacb829ec51e58a92cb5","tid":1537070,"uid":252672,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:01:15.000Z","msg":"有留意過金水係邊個就知唔可信<br />\n只係太多人14年無留意，依家改名又出黎搞搞震"},{"pid":"eb86c448f8a04e007eaab0400f4ab9ffb437fd89","tid":1537070,"uid":267425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:01:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">解散警隊 刻不容緩</span></strong></span><br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2TXKCPJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2TXKCPJ.jpg&h=a6a9f88f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c02f2dcc11d9770f036cc81e8edb5777151a7a7b","tid":1537070,"uid":169396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:01:52.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲同我一樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146ed4922b4a85377dcdc425698812864bf04d78","tid":1537070,"uid":2611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:02:27.000Z","msg":"聽日再開啦 <br />\n利申：有朋友試過俾佢擺上枱"},{"pid":"4b4aaa54416f8473c44be856b5e59c0fcdd06551","tid":1537070,"uid":169396,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d91d6efcdbf1ba49ed9eaacb829ec51e58a92cb5","tid":1537070,"uid":252672,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:01:15.000Z","msg":"有留意過金水係邊個就知唔可信<br />\n只係太多人14年無留意，依家改名又出黎搞搞震"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:02:58.000Z","msg":"日日見到share金水都煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢啲po全部流料黎"},{"pid":"04355ec7adbbe59cfc196ceb1fb7eb51cd889227","tid":15370